Description:
   Solar Brand is the Dawn Liturgy's ritual opener: a mark of the Black Sun
   Shard's authority pressed briefly into a target. In the Solar Court's
   five-office tradition it is taught to all candidates as the first act of
   channeled authority — not a prayer for aid but a direct expression of
   cosmological function.

   Damage: 2d4 + level/4, holy elemental. Against targets of corrupt
   alignment (< -350), damage is increased by 50%. No save against the
   damage. Mana cost: 8. Available automatically at level 1.

   Solar Brand does not scale dramatically with level. Clerics who need
   sustained offensive output should advance to Divine Strike (level 4).
